T1 about 3.0
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as posteriorly broad. T2 about 1.15
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as posteriorly broad. 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="23">Colour</emphasis>
.
